# Portfolio Website (React)

A **responsive, Figma-driven portfolio website** built with **React** and **CSS Modules**, focused on **clean layout architecture, consistent alignment, and mobile-first responsiveness** across mobile, desktop, and 2K screens.

---

## вњЁ Key Highlights

* **Single content rail system** for consistent alignment across Header, Hero, and all sections
* **Responsive navbar**

  * Desktop grid-based nav
  * Mobile hamburger menu with full-screen overlay
  * Social icons included in mobile menu
* **Hero section**

  * Grid-based layout (2 columns в†’ 1 column on mobile)
  * Layered visuals (image, logo behind image, dotted overlay)
  * Figma-matched typography and spacing
* **No horizontal scroll**

  * Fixed widths overridden on mobile
  * Absolute elements safely constrained
* **Scalable architecture**

  * Grid for macro layout
  * Flexbox for micro alignment
  * No duplicated margins or rails

---

## рџ§± Layout System

```css
.content-rail {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1024px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
```

* Rail controls width & centering only
* Spacing handled at layout/component level
* Decorative elements allowed to overflow on desktop only

